<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>We are the UK’s innovation agency.</p>

<p><abbr title="Innovate UK">Innovate UK</abbr> is part of the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/uk-research-and-innovation">UK Research and Innovation</a>.</p>
</div>

