            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
              <p>Email</p>
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="mailto:foi@ukri.org">foi@ukri.org</a></p>
            </div>


            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>If you would like to request personal information under the Data Protection Act, you should submit your request to <a href="mailto:dataprotection@ukri.org" class="brand__color">dataprotection@ukri.org</a> or write to the Data Protection Officer, Head of Information Governance on the address above.</p>
